// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
// Antigravity v2 — Strings Error Test Suite
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
//
// Each file triggers a specific error. Run individually.
//
// 1. .substring() with an invalid range
//    - File: test_errors/err_str_substring.tiny
//    - Expected exit code: 70
//    - Expected:
//      test_errors/err_str_substring.tiny:3:14: Runtime error: Invalid substring range 3 to 10 for string of length 5.
//      show "hello".substring(3, 10)
//                   ^
//
// 2. .charAt() out of bounds
//    - File: test_errors/err_str_charat.tiny
//    - Expected exit code: 70
//    - Expected:
//      test_errors/err_str_charat.tiny:3:14: Runtime error: Index 10 out of bounds for string of length 5.
//      show "hello".charAt(10)
//                   ^
//
// 3. Unknown method call on a string
//    - File: test_errors/err_str_unknown_method.tiny
//    - Expected exit code: 70
//    - Expected:
//      test_errors/err_str_unknown_method.tiny:3:14: Runtime error: String has no method 'foo'.
//      show "hello".foo()
//                   ^
//
// 4. Wrong argument count to a string method
//    - File: test_errors/err_str_arity.tiny
//    - Expected exit code: 70
//    - Expected:
//      test_errors/err_str_arity.tiny:3:14: Runtime error: Method 'length' expects 0 argument(s) but got 1.
//      show "hello".length(42)
//                   ^
//
// 5. Unescaped bad escape sequence
//    - File: test_errors/err_str_bad_escape.tiny
//    - Expected exit code: 65
//    - Expected:
//      test_errors/err_str_bad_escape.tiny:3:6: Lexer error: Invalid escape sequence: \q
//      show "hello \q world"
//           ^
//
// 6. Malformed interpolation expression
//    - File: test_errors/err_str_malformed_interpolation.tiny
//    - Expected exit code: 65
//    - Expected:
//      test_errors/err_str_malformed_interpolation.tiny:4:6: Parse error: at '"hello ${a +} world"': Malformed interpolation expression.
